Welcome to Pesa Mtandaoni! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your personal information when you use our mobile application, Pesa Mtandaoni.

1. Information We Do Not Collect
We do not collect, store, or process any personal data or sensitive information from users of our application. Pesa Mtandaoni does not require you to create an account, log in, or provide any personal information.

2. Advertising
Pesa Mtandaoni uses third-party advertisements to support the application. These ads are provided by third-party ad networks, which may collect information about your device and usage to display relevant ads. The data collected by these ad networks is not accessible to us and is governed by their own privacy policies.

Ad Providers
