3. Security
We are committed to protecting your information and use reasonable security measures to safeguard any data processed by third parties. However, since we do not collect any personal information, we are not directly responsible for the security of any data collected by third-party ad networks.

4. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.

